{"tid":987944,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友一齊沖涼 放左個屁 佢話要分手","createTime":"2019-01-19T16:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T16:56:39.000Z","uid":42446,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"62c06b5f206b8ffbc2a0899bd1bdc2ab12c7c06c","tid":987944,"uid":42446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"頭先同男朋友一齊沖涼<br />\n平時叫佢聞下啲嘢食咩味 成日話自己鼻塞<br />\n諗住佢唔會聞到 咪放左個屁爽下<br />\n<br />\n點知佢聞到 仲問我係咪放屁<br />\n係咁屌話臭到仆街 即刻唔沖衝左出去<br />\n<br />\n到我沖完出返去 佢換好晒衫話要分手 <br />\n我都唔知俾咩反應<br />\n佢就頭也不回出左我屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家係咁氹返佢應承佢以後唔放屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915dcda20335d978c02e09faa928d0bf55c49e42","tid":987944,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"沖涼放屁先正 同啲熱氣一齊攻入鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6768518fde1dbf8b73a20c21c60cb67263728756","tid":987944,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"25d1a23439b36bbd6d89a100f729491132c8943d","tid":987944,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"抵你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566d58fe5587b6cecb1d61dc0eea4250f32cfefc","tid":987944,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab626694264c95b28a58f42be8a90077715fc0d1","tid":9879